## VPN Status Icon
# Select one VPN provider for the status bar icon.
# options: auto, none, wireguard, tailscale
# Leave VPN_PROVIDER unset, or set it to `auto`, to detect Tailscale first and then WireGuard.
# Set VPN_PROVIDER=none to hide the VPN icon entirely.
# VPN_PROVIDER=auto
# When VPN_PROVIDER=wireguard, the status bar shows the VPN icon when the interface below is up.
# Default interface is wg0. Change this if your WireGuard interface has a different name.
# WIREGUARD_INTERFACE=wg0
# When VPN_PROVIDER=tailscale, detection uses `tailscale status --json` and the same VPN icon is shown when connected.
# Set TAILSCALE_COMMAND if `tailscale` is not on PATH for the chatbot service.
# TAILSCALE_COMMAND=/usr/bin/tailscale

